trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty"> </xref> 지정 된 이름 및 값 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The property name.
The property value.
Creates a deep or shallow copy of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty"></xref>.
A shallow copy of a <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> references the same XML element as the original.
trans-unit.target: 단순 복사본을 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>원본과 동일한 XML 요소를 참조 합니다.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>

trans-unit.source: Modifications to the name or value of a shallow copy will be reflected in both copies.
trans-unit.target: 이름이 나 값의 단순 복사본을 수정 두 복사본에 반영 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: However, depending on property evaluation, the two copies could have different <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty.FinalValue%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: 그러나 속성 평가 따라 두 복사본이 있을 수 다른 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty.FinalValue%2A>속성 값.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty.FinalValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: A deep copy of a <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> creates a new XML element to reference so that both copies of the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> can be independently modified.
trans-unit.target: 전체 복사본을 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>의 복사본을 둘 다 있도록 참조를 새 XML 요소를 만듭니다는 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>독립적으로 수정할 수 없습니다.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>
